{
  "__inputs": [],
  "__requires": [
    { "type": "grafana", "id": "grafana", "name": "Grafana", "version": "9.0.0" },
    { "type": "datasource", "id": "prometheus", "name": "Prometheus", "version": "1.0.0" },
    { "type": "panel", "id": "timeseries", "name": "Time series", "version": "" },
    { "type": "panel", "id": "gauge", "name": "Gauge", "version": "" }
  ],
  "annotations": {
    "list": []
  },
  "description": "Golden signals + camada de container para kanban-vision-api: request rate, error rate, latency, pool HikariCP, working set/throttle do container e simulation throughput. O heap (JVM Memory) mede o runtime; o pod e dimensionado pelo working set (ADR-0037).",
  "editable": true,
  "fiscalYearStartMonth": 0,
  "graphTooltip": 1,
  "id": null,
  "links": [],
  "panels": [
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": { "lineWidth": 1, "fillOpacity": 10, "gradientMode": "none" },
          "unit": "reqps"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "legend": { "calcs": ["mean", "max"], "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom" },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "none" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
          "expr": "sum(rate(ktor_http_server_requests_seconds_count[1m])) by (uri, method)",
          "legendFormat": "{{ method }} {{ uri }}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Request Rate (req/s)",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": { "lineWidth": 1, "fillOpacity": 10 },
          "unit": "percentunit",
          "min": 0,
          "max": 1,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 0.01 },
              { "color": "red", "value": 0.05 }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 0 },
      "id": 2,
      "options": {
        "legend": { "calcs": ["mean", "max"], "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom" },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "none" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
          "expr": "sum(rate(ktor_http_server_requests_seconds_count{status=~\"5..\"}[1m])) / sum(rate(ktor_http_server_requests_seconds_count[1m]))",
          "legendFormat": "5xx error rate",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "HTTP Error Rate (5xx %)",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": { "lineWidth": 1, "fillOpacity": 5 },
          "unit": "s"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 8 },
      "id": 3,
      "options": {
        "legend": { "calcs": ["mean", "max"], "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom" },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "none" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.50, sum by (le) (rate(ktor_http_server_requests_seconds_bucket[5m])))",
          "legendFormat": "P50",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by (le) (rate(ktor_http_server_requests_seconds_bucket[5m])))",
          "legendFormat": "P95",
          "refId": "B"
        },
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.99, sum by (le) (rate(ktor_http_server_requests_seconds_bucket[5m])))",
          "legendFormat": "P99",
          "refId": "C"
        }
      ],
      "title": "HTTP Latency P50 / P95 / P99",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "unit": "percentunit",
          "min": 0,
          "max": 1,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 0.7 },
              { "color": "red", "value": 0.9 }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "description": "Utilizacao do pool por instancia. A metrica hikaricp_* so passou a EXISTIR no GAP-BW: o Hikari nunca fora bindado ao Micrometer, entao este painel exibia \"No data\" e o alerta HikariPoolExhaustion nunca podia disparar. NAO ve exaustao de frota -- e por instancia (ver alerta DbConnectionFleetExhaustion).",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 8, "x": 0, "y": 16 },
      "id": 4,
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false },
        "orientation": "auto",
        "showThresholdLabels": false,
        "showThresholdMarkers": true
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
          "expr": "hikaricp_connections_active / hikaricp_connections_max",
          "legendFormat": "Pool utilisation",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "HikariCP Pool Utilisation",
      "type": "gauge"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": { "lineWidth": 1, "fillOpacity": 10 },
          "unit": "bytes"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "description": "Heap/non-heap do runtime. NAO e o sinal de capacidade do pod: no binario nativo o heap e pequeno e nao e devolvido ao SO (ADR-0037). Para dimensionar, use o painel Container Memory -- Working Set.",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 8, "x": 8, "y": 16 },
      "id": 5,
      "options": {
        "legend": { "calcs": ["mean", "max"], "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom" },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "none" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
          "expr": "jvm_memory_used_bytes{area=\"heap\"}",
          "legendFormat": "Heap used",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
          "expr": "jvm_memory_used_bytes{area=\"nonheap\"}",
          "legendFormat": "Non-heap used",
          "refId": "B"
        }
      ],
      "title": "JVM Memory",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": { "lineWidth": 1, "fillOpacity": 10 },
          "unit": "short"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 8, "x": 16, "y": 16 },
      "id": 6,
      "options": {
        "legend": { "calcs": ["mean", "max"], "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom" },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "none" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
          "expr": "rate(kanban_simulation_days_executed_total[1m])",
          "legendFormat": "Simulation days/s",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Simulation Throughput (days/s)",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": { "lineWidth": 1, "fillOpacity": 10 },
          "unit": "short"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 8, "x": 0, "y": 24 },
      "id": 7,
      "options": {
        "legend": { "calcs": ["mean", "max"], "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom" },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "none" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
          "expr": "rate(kanban_card_completed_total[1m])",
          "legendFormat": "Cards/s",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Card Completion Throughput (cards/s)",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "description": "Working set (memory.current - inactive_file) do container contra o limite. E esta metrica -- e NAO memory.peak, que inclui page cache reclaimavel e variou 93<->152 MiB na mesma config -- que governa eviction e dimensiona requests.memory (ADR-0037: p50 55 MiB, max 92 MiB).",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": { "lineWidth": 1, "fillOpacity": 10 },
          "unit": "bytes"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 8, "x": 8, "y": 24 },
      "id": 8,
      "options": {
        "legend": { "calcs": ["mean", "max"], "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom" },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "none" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
          "expr": "container_memory_working_set_bytes{namespace=\"kanban-vision\",container=\"api\"}",
          "legendFormat": "Working set",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
          "expr": "container_spec_memory_limit_bytes{namespace=\"kanban-vision\",container=\"api\"}",
          "legendFormat": "Limite do container",
          "refId": "B"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Container Memory — Working Set vs Limit",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "description": "Fracao dos periodos de CFS estrangulados pelo kernel. Foi o gargalo real do envelope antigo (limits.cpu 500m custava -69% de throughput) e NENHUM alerta o enxergava: throttle nao gera 5xx nem latencia acima do threshold. So tem sinal com limite de CPU aplicado (docker-compose.limits.yml localmente; em k8s o limits.cpu esta sempre la).",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": { "lineWidth": 1, "fillOpacity": 10 },
          "unit": "percentunit"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 8, "x": 16, "y": 24 },
      "id": 9,
      "options": {
        "legend": { "calcs": ["mean", "max"], "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom" },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "none" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
          "expr": "rate(container_cpu_cfs_throttled_periods_total{namespace=\"kanban-vision\",container=\"api\"}[1m]) / (rate(container_cpu_cfs_periods_total{namespace=\"kanban-vision\",container=\"api\"}[1m]) > 0)",
          "legendFormat": "Periodos estrangulados",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Container CPU — Throttled Periods",
      "type": "timeseries"
    }
  ],
  "refresh": "30s",
  "schemaVersion": 38,
  "tags": ["kanban-vision", "golden-signals"],
  "templating": { "list": [] },
  "time": { "from": "now-1h", "to": "now" },
  "timepicker": {},
  "timezone": "browser",
  "title": "Kanban Vision API",
  "uid": "kanban-vision-api",
  "version": 1
}
